item.title: Aspose.BarCode for Python via .NET 22.12
item.description: This page contains the information about the first release note for Aspose.BarCode for Python via .NET 22.12. Aspose has launched the new barcode API called Aspose.BarCode for Python via .NET 22.12. This API is intended to develop cross-platform applications for creating and reading barcodes. It can be installed on Windows and Linux platforms.
